result.title: Yandex.Algorithm-2014: qualification round
result.content:
Weâ€™d like to invite you to take part in the qualification round of the Yandex.Algorithm competition that will start on May 25, 2014, at midnight. You need to start your qualification within 24 hours from the beginning of the qualification round. Qualification will last 100 minutes.

To advance to the next stage of Yandex.Algorithm you will need to solve at least one problem during your qualification.

Participants, already advanced to the elimination stage from warm-up round, are also welcome on the qualification.

Good luck!
